name: Rare Cybop
description: Common Cybops might idolize the Ethereal Jellbilly, but the Rare Cybop is no such admirer! It stalwartly marches (or hovers) to the beat of a different drum, transfiguring its mechanical body to match ancient cave drawings of early Cybops. Non-conformity comes with a price, though: the jostling of its twin engines sometimes results in motion sickness, hence its greenish complexion.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 10 hr 30 min, Enhanced Time: 7 hr 52 min 30 sec
